 Hololive Production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side- 创下2023年VTuber发行最高收视人数纪录https://p2y.jp/hololive-product-countdown-live-20232024-hololive-side-recorded-the-largest-2023-vtuber-streaming-viewers/ https://p2y.jp/hololive-product-countdown-live-20232024-hololive-side-recorded-the-largest-2023-vtuber-streaming-viewers/#respondp2y_admin Sun, 31 Dec 2023 15:33:46 +0000 VTuberバーチャルhololive DEV_ISYouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberホロのぐらふぃてぃ(ホロぐら)ホロライブホロライブEnglish(hololive-EN)ホロライブインドネシア(hololive-ID)ホロライブプロダクション同時視聴者数(同接数) https://p2y.jp/?p=110447 <p> VTuber经纪公司Hololive Production年终现场活动发布“hololive Production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-”[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-countdown-live-20232024-hololive-side-recorded-the-largest-2023-vtuber-streaming-viewers/">Hololive制作后的COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-创下2023年VTuber发行最高收视人数纪录，</a>首次在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上公开。; <p></p><p> VTuber经纪公司Hololive Production的年末直播活动广播“ <strong>hololive Production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2023▷2024 -hololive side-</strong> ”达到了2023年所有VTuber广播中最高的同时观看人数（同时观看人数）（令和5年）。网站统计确认有<strong>268,222 人</strong>被记录。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1100" height="619" data-attachment-id="110450" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-countdown-live-20232024-hololive-side-recorded-the-largest-2023-vtuber-streaming-viewers/hololive_production_countdown_live_2023_2024_hololive_side/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/hololive_production_countdown_live_2023_2024_hololive_side.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&